title: Britney Spears ***The complete Recording that she lip syncs to o
description:
I Know this isnt a KISS release like I normally upload. I did however find this to be a very interesting find. I had this sent to me about a month ago. The only thing in the note was that this was the recording that Britney spears plays every night on her "Circus tour" to lip sync and dance to. 

Its been debated many times weather she actually sings or not on tour. Then again to most it was never a surprise that she didn't. Some ppl dont care, because lets face it she is a great dancer. For better or for worse this the complete tape of the concert night after night that she lip syncs and dances too.

set list is below:


1.Intro (welcome to the circus)

2. Circus

3. Piece Of Me

4. Radar

5. Gimme More

6. Ooh Ooh Baby

7. Hot as ice

8. Boys

9. If u seek amy

10. Me against the music

11. Everytime

12. Sweet Dreams

13. Freak Show 

14. Get Naked

15. Mannequin

16. Intro & Breath on me

17. Touch of my hand

18. Do somethin

19. Im slave 4 U

20. Dancers segue mix

21. Toxic

22. Baby one more time

23.(Interlude)Break the ice

24. Womanizer

25. Final (Womanizer)



***Note*** These are all the actual concert mixes for the current tour. This is the actual tape used every night on her current tour. 

If your a Britney Spears fan do enjoy and remember to seed!!

Sharing is caring!!
